	<entry>
		<title>osgvolume</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.openscenegraph.com/index.php/documentation/guides/user-guides/58-osgvolume"/>
		<published>2012-09-12T22:35:24+00:00</published>
		<updated>2012-09-12T22:35:24+00:00</updated>
		<id>https://www.openscenegraph.com/index.php/documentation/guides/user-guides/58-osgvolume</id>
		<author>
			<name>openscenegraph</name>
			<email>jtorresfabra@gmail.com</email>
		</author>
		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Demonstrates OSG's volume rendering capabilities. Needs a list of 2D images, or a 3D image (.dds)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Program arguments&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;table class=&quot;withborder&quot;&gt;
&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;strong&gt;argument&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;strong&gt;description&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;strong&gt; default &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;--alphaFunc&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt; &lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;0.02&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;--clip &amp;lt;ratio&amp;gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;clip volume as a ratio, 0.0 clip all, 1.0 clip none.&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;1.0&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;--compressed&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Enable the usage of compressed textures.&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt; &lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;--compressed-arb&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Enable the usage of OpenGL ARB compressed textures&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt; &lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;--compressed-dxt1&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Enable the usage of S3TC DXT1 compressed textures.&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt; &lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;--compressed-dxt3&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Enable the usage of S3TC DXT3 compressed textures.&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt; &lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
